# Private local-only files that must never be committed to this public
# repo. The `.wav` originals, the .docx/.pdf dist formats, and the
# ACE-Step prompt-writing book all live under
# `C:\Users\Administrator\rAIdio-private\` on the maintainer's machine
# and are published via different channels (MP3 demos are committed;
# raw WAV originals and dist formats are not).

# Lossless audio originals — only MP3 demos are published.
*.wav

# Distribution formats — the manual is the .md files here; .docx/.pdf
# builds are local artefacts only.
*.docx
*.pdf

# Drafts kept private until launch.
writing-prompts-*.md

# Editor / OS cruft
.vscode/
.idea/
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
